{
  "stem": "21582.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, beautiful.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were just, as I said, completely covered with scabies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we-- during-- and, oh-- how we were clad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had wooden clogs and barefoot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember when we used to walk on ice, the clogs would kind of slash and always cut.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I always had these deep cuts, all of my whole leg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The inside my legs were covered with-- with scabs and oozing scabs and scabies and mange.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, I used a-- the [NON-ENGLISH], the can, to urinate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I opened the door, I looked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I poured the urine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the Jewish couple, Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Aronovitz. ?] He-- he was OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He caught me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he jumped on the bunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was whipping me with-- with the whip, with the-- he was just whipping me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother flung her itself to protect me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She flung herself to cover me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then my mother could be very dramatic, and but-- but her drama was sincere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she said to him, you know, my blood will not rest in the grave for what you're doing to my child.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it will haunt you wherever you'll go for the rest of your life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, you would say, my goodness, what a horrendous person he was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But you have to also recognize that at the same time we had lots of rats and mice in camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the same-- the same commander, of the-- the [NON-ENGLISH] that [? sadist, ?] he gave orders that each kapo-- there were several kapos of each section-- had to deliver a certain amount of mice, a certain amount of rats.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because he wanted the camp to be free of rats.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
